    <text>
        <body>
            <div>

                <pb facs="liv_001347_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName><geogName type="island">Expedition Island</geogName></placeName> 
<lb/><date when="1858-08-13">13 August
<lb/>1858</date></dateline></opener>
<lb/><p rend="center"><measure>Longitude 35Â°-51'-09" E</measure></p>
<lb/><p>On this Island the <orgName><placeName><geogName type="river">Zambesi</geogName></placeName> <!-- geog: Expedition Island -->
<lb/>Expedition</orgName> under <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> 
<lb/>Livingstone</persName> erected their
<lb/>iron house and deposited
<lb/>their luggage till by
<lb/>five successive trips
<lb/>the Ma Robert steam
<lb/>Launch removed it
<lb/>up the river. At this <!-- geog: Zambesi -->
<lb/>log of <foreign xml:lang="la"><hi rend="underline">lignum vitae</hi></foreign> <add place="above" hand="#U">(1)</add>
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> <hi rend="underline">Francis Skead</hi></persName> <choice><abbr>R.N.</abbr><expan>Royal Navy</expan></choice> <add place="above" hand ="#U">(2)</add>
<lb/>observed for the latitude
<lb/>and Longitude</p>

                <pb facs="liv_001347_0002" n="0002"/>
<!-- A gap of about 6 lines here - need to check if this is the right way to code this AM --><!-- Yup, it is! HB -->
<lb/><space extent="6" unit="lines" dim="vertical"/>
<lb/><!-- vertical line in left margin (probably in the same hand as the (1) (2) & (3)) marks out whole of next paragraph AM --><p rend="no-indent"><add place="marginleft" hand="#U"><metamark/></add> <add place="above" hand="#U">(3)</add> At a tree about <measure>300 <choice><abbr>yds</abbr><expan>yards</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Mag.</abbr><expan>Magnetic</expan></choice> North</measure>
<lb/>marked with the broad arrow
<lb/>and the letter M <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Charles
<lb/>Livingstone</persName> took sets of
<lb/>observations for Magnetical
<lb/>dip. deflection, vibration
<lb/><add place="marginleft" hand="#U">(3)</add> and declination</p>
<lb/><p>On this day the <orgName>Expedition</orgName>
<lb/>finally quits the island <!-- geog: Expedition Island -->
<lb/>to go first to <placeName><settlement type="village">Shupanga</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>and thence to <placeName><settlement type="town">Tete</settlement></placeName>.

                <pb facs="liv_001347_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>It is hoped that about three
<lb/>trips will suffice to land
<lb/>all the <orgName>Expedition</orgName> at <placeName><settlement type="town">Tete</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>some machinery and stores
<lb/>will be left at <placeName><settlement type="village">Shupanga</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>and <placeName><settlement type="town">Senna</settlement></placeName> <add place="inline" hand="#U">(4)</add></p>
<lb/><p>All the members of 
<lb/>the <orgName>Expedition</orgName> have
<lb/>enjoyed good health
<lb/>- ever since our arrival
<lb/>in the <placeName><region>Delta</region></placeName> in the 
<lb/>middle of <date when="1858-05">May last</date>.
<lb/>All except one have
<lb/>taken small doses
<lb/>of <term type="medicament">quinine</term> daily.
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Baines</persName> suffers
<lb/>a little at present

                <pb facs="liv_001347_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>a slight <term type="ailment">stroke of the sun</term>.
<lb/><add place="marginleft" hand="#U">(5)</add><add hand="#U"><metamark/></add><!-- underlining, probably in the same unknown hand as the numbering, also marks out this section between the (5) markers AM --> The country has been in <!-- geog:  -->
<lb/>a state of war ever
<lb/>since we came but
<lb/>no party ever molested
<lb/>us - <add place="inline" hand="#U">(5)</add> We have had
<lb/>intercourse with both
<lb/><add place="inline" hand="#U">(6)</add><add hand="#U"><metamark/></add><!-- underlining, probably in the same unknown hand as the numbering, also marks out this section between the (6) markers except the words "are termed rebels" which are not underlined - AM --> <term type="people">Portuguese</term> and what
<lb/>are termed rebels
<lb/>without offence <add place="above" hand="#U">(6)</add></p>
<lb/><p>We propose to come
<lb/>down from <placeName><settlement type="town">Tete</settlement></placeName> to the
<lb/>mouth of the <placeName><geogName type="river">Kongone</geogName></placeName> so as
<lb/>to be there on <date when="1858-12-25">Christmas day
<lb/>next</date> to <choice><sic>recieve</sic><corr>receive</corr></choice> &amp; deliver
<lb/>despatches</p> <closer><signed>David Livingstone
<lb/><term type="occupation"><choice><abbr>H.M<supplied cert="high">.</supplied></abbr><expan>Her Majesty's</expan></choice> Consul</term>.</signed></closer>              

            </div>
